title: Kavanagh QC Season 1
description:
Kavanagh QC was a British television series made by Carlton Television for ITV between 1995 and 2001. The series starred John Thaw as the brilliant criminal law barrister James Kavanagh QC who comes from a working class upbringing in Bolton, Lancashire. This is only discovered in later episodes as his parents' health deteriorates and through an exchange with a colleague who presumed that Kavanagh was actually a Yorkshireman.
